    <briefdescription>
<para>This file illustrates update multiboot pdi. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>To build this application, xilmailbox library must be included in BSP and xilloader library must be in client mode</para><para>This example is supported for Versal and Versal Net devices.</para><para><heading level="2">Procedure to run the example. </heading>
</para><para>Load full Pdi. Download the secondary pdi into ddr. In serial sf probe 0 0 0 sf erase &lt;offset&gt; &lt;size of=&quot;&quot; pdi&gt;=&quot;&quot;&gt; sf write &lt;ddr address&gt;=&quot;&quot;&gt; &lt;offset&gt; &lt;size of=&quot;&quot; pdi&gt;=&quot;&quot;&gt; In xsdb mwr -force 0xF1110004 &lt;offset value/0x8000&gt; mrd -force 0xF1110004 change the bootmode.</para><para><preformatted>
MODIFICATION HISTORY:</preformatted></para><para><preformatted>Ver   Who  Date     Changes
